c Service Request or a Tour Guide or Tour Buddy may be reported not beyond 24 hours from when the Services were availed. In case the issue or grievance is criminal in nature, the complaint may be filed within 72 hours of the event/availing the Service. Any complaint, dispute or grievance in relation to the Services should be addressed to Voyease as given below. Such complaint, dispute or grievance will be handled as per applicable laws. Grievance Officer: Pankaj Sharma e-mail: pankaj@Voyease.in Address: CK-13/94, Bajrang Katra, Pashupateshwar, Chowk, Varanasi-221001, India B. SPECIAL TERMS In addition to the General Terms, along with any other agreements or documents executed / accepted by you, the following additional special terms (\u201CSpecial Terms\u201D) apply to your use of certain specific Services. RELIGIOUS SERVICES Provision of Contact Information: The Company\u2019s role is limited to providing you with the contact information of Panditjis available in your selected location upon receipt of the payment. The Company does not participate in any service agreement between you and the Panditji. No Guarantee of Services: The Company does not guarantee the availability, quality, or conduct of any services offered by the Panditji. All arrangements and negotiations for the performance of religious ceremonies or rituals are between you and the Panditji. No Liability for Services Rendered: The Company will not be held liable for any issues or disputes arising from the services provided by the Panditji, including but not limited to service quality, fees charged, or any other terms agreed upon between you and the Panditji. Non-Refundable Fees: The fee collected by the Company for providing the contact details of the Panditji is non-refundable, regardless of whether the service is utilized or not. Independent Contractors: Panditjis are independent contractors and not employees, agents, or representatives of the Company. The Company does not endorse, recommend, or guarantee any specific Panditji or their services. OTHER SERVICES Platform for Displaying Local Shops: VoyEase provides a platform to display information about various local shops (\u201CLocal Shops\u201D) for the user\u2019s convenience. This information is offered by third-party shops (\u201CLocal Shop Vendors\u201D). Limited Role of VoyEase: The Company\u2019s role is limited to displaying information about the Local Shops. VoyEase does not engage in any transactions, sales, or services offered by the Local Shop Vendors. No Endorsement: The Company does not endorse, recommend, or guarantee the quality or authenticity of any products or services offered by the Local Shops. The relationship between the user and the Local Shop Vendors is strictly between those parties. No Liability: VoyEase will not be held liable for any disputes, damages, or losses that may arise from the user\u2019s interaction with the Local Shop Vendors. The user assumes full responsibility for any transactions or engagements with the Local Shops."
