All rights not otherwise claimed under these Terms or by the Company are hereby reserved. The information contained in this Platform is intended solely to provide general information for the personal use of the reader, who accepts full responsibility for its use.
The Company does not represent or endorse the accuracy or reliability of any information or advertisement contained on, distributed through, linked, downloaded, or accessed from any of the services contained on this Platform, or the quality of any products, information, or other materials displayed or obtained by you as a result of any product, information, or other materials displayed, or obtained by you as a result of an advertisement or any other information or offer in or in connection with a Service.
